sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant External as External Network
    participant iptables as iptables (Pod Kernel)
    participant Proxy as Sidecar Proxy (Envoy)
    participant App as App Container (Localhost)

    Note over iptables, Proxy: INCOMING TRAFFIC FLOW
    External->>iptables: Packet sent to Pod IP:Port (e.g. 80)
    iptables->>Proxy: PREROUTING rule redirects to Proxy Port 15006
    Proxy->>Proxy: Validates mTLS & Auth Policies
    Proxy->>App: Forwards decrypted packet to localhost:80
    App-->>Proxy: Sends response headers/data

    Note over iptables, Proxy: OUTGOING TRAFFIC FLOW
    App->>iptables: App sends outbound request to External IP
    iptables->>Proxy: OUTPUT rule redirects to Proxy Port 15001
    Proxy->>Proxy: Resolves target endpoint & creates mTLS session
    Proxy->>External: Forwards encrypted request to destination
